@node "SystemDatas" "System Datas"


                      @{b}SystemEditor: System Datas Window
                     ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~@{ub}

@{u}Introduction@{uu}

The System Datas Window is to configure global bbs data. Everything you can
configure here will take effect on all nodes and everything else on your BBS.

                @{"      BBS Name        " link "SESysDatBBSName"} @{"      Userlimit       " link "SESysDatUserlimit"}
                @{"     BBS Origin       " link "SESysDatBBSOrigin"} @{"   Max Name Failure   " link "SESysDatMaxNameFailure"}
                @{"     SysOp Name       " link "SESysDatSysOpName"} @{"  Max UserPW Failure  " link "SESysDatMaxUserPWFailure"}
                @{"  BBS Location Path   " link "SESysDatBBSLocationPath"} @{"  Max SysPW Failure   " link "SESysDatMaxSysPWFailure"}
                @{"  UserData/Key Path   " link "SESysDatUserDataKeyPath"} @{"   Max NUP Failure    " link "SESysDatMaxNUPFailure"}
                @{"    UserData Name     " link "SESysDatUserDataName"} @{"    Max User Hacks    " link "SESysDatMaxUserHacks"}
                @{"    UserKeys Name     " link "SESysDatUserKeysName"} @{" Do on Max User Hacks " link "SESysDatDoonMaxUserHacks"}
                @{"    File Crypt PW     " link "SESysDatFileCryptPW"} @{"     EmergencyPW      " link "SESysDatEmergencyPW"}
                @{"    NewUser Level     " link "SESysDatNewUserLevel"} @{"     FileNumbers      " link "SESysDatFileNumbers"}
                @{"    Show Bull.txt     " link "SESysDatShowBulltxt"} @{"    Date and Bytes    " link "SESysDatDateandBytes"}
                @{"  Bull Min NumLines   " link "SESysDatBullMinNumLines"} @{"  Allow UserFileBase  " link "SESysDatAllowUserFileBase"}
                @{"   Min Break Level    " link "SESysDatMinBreakLevel"} @{"   Do File Descripts  " link "SESysDatDoFileDescripts"}
                @{"   UPWFail UEALLLvl   " link "SESysDatUPWFailUEALLLvl"} @{"       Text WHO       " link "SESysDatTextWHO"}
                @{"  FileDescUnderLine   " link "SESysDatFileDescUnderLine"} @{"     MultiNodeUser    " link "SESysDatMultiNodeUser"}
                @{"     Def NumLines     " link "SESysDatDefNumLines"} @{"    Right Filenames   " link "SESysDatRightFilenames"}
                @{"   Number of Nodes    " link "SESysDatNumberofNodes"} @{"  MsgCryPW MsgHeader  " link "SESysDatMsgCryPWMsgHeader"}
                @{"  FileCryPW FileList  " link "SESysDatFileCryPWFileList"} @{"     Auto Restrict    " link "SESysDatAutoRestrict"}
                @{"    Max Fid Lines     " link "SESysDatMaxFidLines"}

                             @{"  MORE System Datas   " link "MoreSystemDatas"}
