@node "SEMNodeIBatchStackSize" "BatchStackSize"


                 @{b}SystemEditor (More Node Edit I): BatchStackSize
                ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~@{ub}

The stack size for batch files. (Used by tools).

@endnode

