                 @{b}SystemEditor (More Node Edit I): Batch Priority
                ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~@{ub}

The prority for batch files. (Used by tools).

