@node "SEConfSAVE" "SAVE"


                       @{b}SystemEditor (Conferences): SAVE
                      ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~@{ub}

Save the settings/changes.

@endnode

