@endnode

@REM==============================================================================

@node "SEDPortNamRexxDoorPort" "RexxDoorPort"


                  @{b}SystemEditor (Door Port Names): RexxDoorPort
                 ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~@{ub}

The RexxDoorPort name for the Nodes Arexx-Ports.

Default: 'FAMERexxPort.'

Note: The Nodenumber will be added to the port name !

      Examples: - FAMERexxPort.<x>     <x> = Nodenumber
                - FAMERexxPort.1         1 = Node 1

Note: There is no need to change this port name.
      It's recommended to leave the default name.

@endnode

@REM==============================================================================

@node "SEDPortNamServerDoorPort" "ServerDoorPort"


                 @{b}SystemEditor (Door Port Names): ServerDoorPort
                ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~@{ub}

