                    @{b}SystemEditor (Door Port Names): ToolPort
                   ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~@{ub}

The ToolPort name is used for the ToolPort of the @{"Server" link "Server.guide/Main"}.

Default: 'FAMEToolPort'

Note: There is no need to change this port name.
      It's recommended to leave the default name.

